248:#| fig-cap: "Median total QALYs across the evidence-stance range, 100,000 draws per point, seed 0. The stance interpolates each tier's credibility mean piecewise-linearly from a near-RCT-only floor (non-randomized tiers at mean 0.01; randomized tier at its drafted mean) through the drafted best-guess tiers (0.5) to near face value (all means 0.999). A scenario path, not a bound; tier concentrations are held fixed."
252:def stance_median(s_val, n=100_000):
256:        floor = base if name == "randomized" else 0.01
257:        m = floor + (s_val/0.5)*(base-floor) if s_val <= 0.5 else base + ((s_val-0.5)/0.5)*(0.999-base)
258:        t["mean"] = min(max(m, 0.001), 0.999)
259:    r = run(p, n=n, seed=0)
